OL,5,G1930 Nations Championship
OL,6,     FArgentina v England (Kick-off
OL,7,     F8.10pm). Jill Douglas presents all
OL,8,     Fthe action from the round-robin
OL,9,     Frugby union match at Estadio Unico
OL,10,     FMadre de Ciudades in Santiago del
OL,11,     FEstero. This is the final contest
OL,12,     Fof the Southern Hemisphere Series,
OL,13,     Fwith three more rounds of
OL,14,     Fround-robin fixtures taking place
OL,15,     Fin the Northern Hemisphere Series
OL,16,     Fin November, before a Finals
OL,17,     FWeekend takes place at the end of
OL,18,     Fthat month in London. England will
OL,19,     Fbe looking for a repeat of their
OL,20,     Flast trip to Argentina in 2025
OL,21,     Fwhen they won both their Test
OL,22,     Fmatches. With analysis from Danny
